Please consult "http://www.hznet.de/dns/zkt/" to get more infos about zkt.

Build 
a) Create a directory for zkt
	$ mkdir zkt-0.5

b) Change to dir
	$ cd zkt-0.5

c) Get current version of zkt
	$ wget http://www.hznet.de/dns/zkt/zkt-0.5.tar 

d) Unpack
	$ tar xvf zkt-0.5.tar

e) Change INSTALLDIR in Makefile (def: $HOME/bin/)

f) Edit config.h	(optional)
		set path of BIND dnssec tools (def: /usr/local/bin/)
		set path of default dnssec.conf file (def: /var/named/)

g) Compile
	$ make

h) Install
	$ make install

i) Install default dnssec.conf file (Optional)
	$ ./dnssec-zkt -c "" -Z > /var/named/dnssec.conf
